text: Cameron Thane Muncey (born 8 February 1980) is an Australian guitarist and vocalist. he is the most important lead guitarist and one of the songwriters of Melbourne-based rock band Jet which formed in 2001MacKenzieSpencer et al., (2007) JET entry.
